=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ El.\">El.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1173</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πάντα βορβόρῳ πεφυρμένα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0260.tlg001:7:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Semon.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.3</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἱστίον . . πεφυρμένον πρινὸς ἄνθεϊ</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">stained, dyed,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0261.tlg001:54\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Simon.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">54</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: dub. in signf. of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φυράω, ἐλαίῳ ἄλφιτα πεφυρμένα,</foreign> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">v.l. for</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">πεφυραμένα</ref> </xr> in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:49\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.49</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τέφρᾳ πεφυρμένῃ ὄξει,</foreign> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">v.l. for</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">πεφυραμένῃ</ref> </xr> in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gp.\">Gp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.39.2</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n112661.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of dry things, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κόνει φύρουσα . . κάρα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg007.perseus-grc1:496\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <tit